criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  age > 18 years;

          -  French social security system affiliation or equivalent;

          -  Patient with an aggressive cutaneous lymphoma (PCDLBCL-LT, mycosis fungoides, T helper
             follicular cutaneous lymphoma) diagnosed and monitored at the university hospital of
             Bordeaux;

          -  Written and informed consent obtained for genetic blood test;

          -  Biopsy sample available for molecular analysis.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Another cancer (except "in situ" and surgery treated cutaneous carcinomas) in the
             precedent 5 years.
